<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٧-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا أَبُو بَكْرٍ الْمَرْوَزِيُّ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">سُئِلَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ:</span> هَلْ خَتَنَ إِبْرَاهِيمُ نَفْسَهُ بِقَدُومٍ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> طَرَفُ الْقَدُومِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>